Subject: [PATCH 08/78] Platform/Sgi: Enable auto generation of PCIE Table

Add the support to auto generate and install PCIE SSDT table from the
data passed from earlier boot components.

Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
